help.content:
Namaste! Main `{bot}` hun, [`Lavamusic`](https://github.com/bongodevs/lavamusic) aur `Discord.js` se bana ek music bot.
Kisi command ke baare mein adhik jankari prapt karne ke liye aap `{prefix}help <command>` ka upyog kar sakte hain.
